title: 3.49- The Egyptian Expedition
itunes:title: 3.49- The Egyptian Expedition
description: In July 1798 Bonaparte and his healthy, hopeful army arrived in Egypt. In August 1799 Bonaparte ditched his now demoralized, plague-ridden army and sailed for home.
